  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Displacement Tracking Matrix</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to continue the implementation of IOM&#x2019;s Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM) in Cabo Delgado Province (Mozambique). In order to do so, IOM continues to provide the humanitarian community and relevant partners with up-to-date and reliable information on the number of displaced persons as well as their needs on a six-week basis. In particular, IOM carries out data collection through baseline-area assessments with key informants at the provincial and district level. DTM teams on the ground also conduct site assessments in the locations previously identified to ensure that multi-sectorial needs including vulnerabilities will be captured.</narrative>
  </description>
